<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Daby English Expressions</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- Google Fonts - Inter -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght=300;400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #1a202c; /* Dark background inspired by Netflix */
            background-image: radial-gradient(at 50% 0%, rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%),
                              radial-gradient(at 0% 100%, rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            color: #e2e8f0; /* Light gray text for contrast */
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 960px; /* Increased max-width for better content display */
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }
        .lesson-card {
            background-color: #2d3748; /* Slightly lighter dark background for cards */
            border-radius: 1rem; /* Rounded corners */
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); /* Deeper shadow */
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        .lesson-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .headline {
            color: #ef4444; /* McDonald's/Burger King Red */
            font-weight: 800; /* Extra bold */
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .sub-headline {
            color: #facc15; /* McDonald's/Burger King Yellow */
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .highlight-text {
            color: #f87171; /* Lighter red for emphasis */
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .example-box {
            background-color: #4a5568; /* Darker gray for example boxes */
            padding: 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border-left: 5px solid #facc15; /* Yellow border for emphasis */
        }
        .answer-reveal {
            background-color: #10b981; /* Green for correct answers */
            color: #1a202c; /* Dark text on green */
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            opacity: 0;
            max-height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease-out, max-height 0.5s ease-out;
        }
        .answer-reveal.show {
            opacity: 1;
            max-height: 100px; /* Adjust as needed to fit content */
        }
        .check-answer-btn {
            background-color: #facc15; /* Yellow button */
            color: #1a202c; /* Dark text */
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 9999px; /* Fully rounded */
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out, transform 0.2s ease-in-out;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .check-answer-btn:hover {
            background-color: #fbbf24; /* Lighter yellow on hover */
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .input-field {
            background-color: #4a5568;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        .input-field:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #facc15;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #1a202c;
            color: #a0aec0;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: auto; /* Pushes footer to the bottom */
            border-top: 1px solid #2d3748;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-center my-8 headline">
            Daby English Expressions
        </h1>
        <p class="text-center text-lg mb-12 text-gray-300">
            Bem-vindo(a) ao seu guia para dominar expressões essenciais em inglês no ambiente de trabalho e no dia a dia! Vamos aprender juntos de forma prática e eficaz.
        </p>

